<title>The Description View</title>
<anchor role="helpid" id="editDescriptionDialogContextId">The Description View</anchor>
  <para>
    The description view is placed in the lower right hand corner of the 
    Specification Perspective when it is opened. The description 
    view displays the text of any descriptions you have added for 
    Test Cases, Test Suites and Test Jobs. 
  </para>
</section>